{%- import "macros/svgs.jinja" as svg -%}

{%- set show_announcement = false %}
{%- macro announcement() %}
<div class="alert bg-info alert-dismissible fade show" style="color: #023d6b;" role="alert">
  <h4 class="alert-heading">       
    {{ svg.announcement_svg | safe }}
    <span class="align-middle">Temporary service interruption during infrastructure maintenance</span>
  </h4>
  During maintenance of the underlying cloud infrastructure on 28.05.2026, an unexpected networking issue caused a temporary interruption of our services. Connectivity was restored by the infrastructure provider during the afternoon, and our service was fully available again around 4:45 PM. We apologize for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience.
</div>
{%- endmacro %}
